Georgia Schmidt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Georgia_Schmidt 0 Georgia Schmidt (August 26, 1904 – April 18, 1997) was an American actress of German descent. Schmidt was the original voice of the Mrs. Beasley doll made by Mattel. She is probably best known as playing the first Talosian alien in the first episode of the original Star Trek series titled "The Cage", later aired as "The Menagerie" in 1966.
